    Items",events:{click(e,t){app.miscGrid.sortItems(((e,t)=>Wb.mixCompare(e.data.code,t.data.code)))}}}]},{cname:"component",textSelectable:false,html:"<div>Feature
    List:</div>\n<ul>\n  <li>Columns sortable, resizable, draggable and freezable.</li>\n  <li>Arbitrary
